SPECIFICATION:
  Background: μ(d,y) = exp(β₀ + γ·log(pop) + δ·poverty_decimal + Σ β_year)
             (poverty_decimal = poverty_rate/100, range 0.017-0.437)
  Triggering: α(marks) = exp(β₀_trig + β_violence·violent + β_state·intervention)
  Kernel: g(t) = exp(-β·t)
  Intensity: λ(t) = μ(d,y) + Σ α(marks_i)·g(t-t_i)

